<s> The idea is _every_ start tag uses NET rather than TAGC, unless we want to make explicit that it is EMPTY.  </s>
<s> My understanding is that an element which is begun with a NET enabling start tag may be closed with an un-minimized close tag as well as a NET.  </s>
